nodes.text: The Galactic League was a major shockball competition that was competed during the last years of the Galactic Republic. In 26 BBY, the Commenor Diamonds defeated the Kuat Artisans in the final to win the League. The following year, the Kuat Artisans were victorious and won the League as a result of the efforts of their star players Gettle Tebron and Kob Mondray.
